Company Overview of Charter Communications Properties LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Charter Communications Properties LLC, doing business as Charter Communications, operates cable networks and provides cable services. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is based in St. Louis, Missouri. Charter Communications Properties LLC operates as a subsidiary of Charter Communications Operating, LLC.


12405 Powerscourt DriveSt. Louis, MO 63131-3674United StatesFounded in 1997



Phone: 303-323-1423

Fax: 303-323-1313








